[30;1m99 | [0m[35m# Github & PyPi[0m
[30;1m100 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m101 | [0m[35mTo force a release the git version needs to be tagged.[0m
[30;1m102 | [0m[35m1) Update `cargo.toml` version[0m
[30;1m103 | [0m[35m2) Update `Releases.md` file[0m
[30;1m104 | [0m[35m3) push code up to repo. Otherwise GitHub won't figure out that the software has been updated.[0m
[30;1m105 | [0m[35m4) Update git `tag` and push. Otherwise the GitHub action `release` will not be triggered.[0m
